      "text": "（くぅー眠い！　眠過ぎるよー！）\n（テスト前だし世界史の授業聞かなきゃなのに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh‚ I'm so sleepy! Way too sleepy!）\n（I have to listen to world history since exams are coming‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（夜中まで雫ちゃんと指相撲した弊害が）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（but the side effects of thumb wrestling with Shizuku-chan）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
