      "text": "（こんな所で訪れるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（until late last night are hitting me now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_skr_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "（……今の私は全身睡魔。少しでも目を閉じると）\n（眠ってしまう眠れる森のアイドル）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Right now‚ I'm being consumed by the Sleep Demon! If I close my eyes）\n（even for a bit‚ I'll fall asleep. I'm a Sleeping Beauty Idol.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（はっ……ここまでくると）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Wait… come to think of it‚）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5
    },
    {
